reviews/originality/2026-05-26-every-path-needs-what-its-teaching-dissolves-daeecdbd22658370.md:47:- Jack Engler interview, You Must Be Somebody Before You Can Be Nobody, Inquiring Mind, https://inquiringmind.com/article/0501_1_engler-interview/: overlap: Very close. Engler says meditation requires ego strength, self-observation, and affect tolerance before no-self can be safely practiced.; difference: Engler's frame is Buddhist psychology and psychotherapy. He does not build a comparative typology of causal continuity, ontological identity, temporal collapse, and divine restoration across traditions.; novelty impact: High reduction. The core minimum-self prerequisite is already a well-known practitioner-facing thesis.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-every-path-needs-what-its-teaching-dissolves-daeecdbd22658370.md:48:- Pudgalavada Buddhist Philosophy, Internet Encyclopedia of Philosophy, https://iep.utm.edu/pudgalavada-buddhist-philosophy/: overlap: Very close historical prior art. Pudgalavadins argued that karma, rebirth, liberation, benevolence, and lived personhood strain a strict no-self aggregate account.; difference: This is an intra-Buddhist metaphysical and doctrinal dispute, not a general model of practice architecture across traditions.; novelty impact: High reduction. The pressure between no-self and soteriological functioning is ancient, not newly discovered.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-every-path-needs-what-its-teaching-dissolves-daeecdbd22658370.md:51:- Not-Self Sutra, Barre Center for Buddhist Studies, https://www.buddhistinquiry.org/article/not-self-sutra/: overlap: Extremely close for the Buddhist unit. It speaks of functional or enactive self, minimal self, agency without ownership, and discipline through causes and conditions.; difference: It is a contemporary Buddhist exposition rather than a cross-tradition predictive model.; novelty impact: High reduction. Parts of the Lumenary wording risk being a renamed Buddhist functional-self account.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-every-path-needs-what-its-teaching-dissolves-daeecdbd22658370.md:52:- Pattern Theory of Selflessness, Mindfulness, https://link.springer.com/article/10.1007/s12671-024-02418-2: overlap: Close contemporary theory. It distinguishes minimal self, ownership, agency, self-pattern, and how meditation transforms self-processes toward selflessness.; difference: It is cognitive-scientific and Buddhist-psychological rather than a primary-text comparative architecture model.; novelty impact: Moderate to high reduction for the minimal-self and practice-transformation language.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-every-path-needs-what-its-teaching-dissolves-daeecdbd22658370.md:53:- Dogen practice-realization sources, for example Soto and Bendowa summaries, https://zenlineage.org/schools/soto and https://buddhismnow.com/2023/10/08/practice-within-realisation-dogen/: overlap: The temporal-collapse strategy is already central to Dogen's practice-realization, where practice is not merely a means to later awakening.; difference: It does not compare this strategy against Advaita, Theravada, and Sufi models of self-continuity.; novelty impact: Moderate reduction. The Zen strategy is known; the comparative placement may still be useful.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-every-path-needs-what-its-teaching-dissolves-daeecdbd22658370.md:57:Unlike Engler, Pudgalavada debates, Collins, or functional-self Buddhist psychology, this idea treats the minimum self as a comparative architecture variable across traditions and claims it predicts effort, verification, warnings, and fruit.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-every-path-needs-what-its-teaching-dissolves-daeecdbd22658370.md:61:Candidate: Other-power and direct-introduction traditions, such as Jodo Shinshu entrusting and Dzogchen pointing-out, appear to minimize self-powered agency while still functioning as paths.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-every-path-needs-what-its-teaching-dissolves-daeecdbd22658370.md:63:Why it strains the model: If a tradition can produce stable transformation through vow, grace, devotion, direct introduction, or teacher-field participation with very little reflexive self-management, then the minimum self may not be an architectural driver. The model would need a scale of required self-capacities rather than a universal requirement.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-every-path-needs-what-its-teaching-dissolves-daeecdbd22658370.md:65:Confidence effect: Lowers confidence in the universal form of the claim. It supports a revised model where paths require some functional receiving capacity, but the amount and role vary sharply.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-every-path-needs-what-its-teaching-dissolves-daeecdbd22658370.md:69:- If: The stronger a path's final self-dissolution claim, the more explicit its safeguards should be against premature or distorted self-loss. Then: Manuals and teachers should warn against nihilism, dissociation, spiritual bypassing, false attainment, antinomianism, or ego-inflation in ways that match the path's self-management strategy. Weakens if: Warnings show no relationship to self-teaching and track only institution, teacher personality, or general ethics. Test surface: Coded comparison of Theravada, Zen, Dzogchen, Advaita, Sufi, Christian apophatic, and Pure Land training materials.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-every-path-needs-what-its-teaching-dissolves-daeecdbd22658370.md:70:- If: Long, effortful paths should develop more elaborate continuity mechanisms than sudden or other-power paths. Then: Theravada stages, Sufi stations, and Advaita preparation should specify capacities, sequence, and error correction; sudden methods should shift burden to teacher recognition, pointing-out, vows, or post-recognition integration. Weakens if: Practice length and self-continuity machinery are unrelated, or sudden paths have equally elaborate minimum-self architecture before recognition. Test surface: Comparative coding of practice sequences, teacher-student protocols, and attainment verification.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-every-path-needs-what-its-teaching-dissolves-daeecdbd22658370.md:71:- If: Dual-trained practitioners should report different kinds of permitted selfhood when switching methods. Then: Vipassana permits causal observation without ownership; Advaita permits witness or Self recognition; Soto Zen discourages gaining selfhood; Sufi practice permits surrendering agency into relation with God. Weakens if: Practitioners report no stable shift, or the shifts are better explained by temperament and teacher style. Test surface: Structured interviews with practitioners trained in two or more lineages.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-every-path-needs-what-its-teaching-dissolves-daeecdbd22658370.md:72:- If: The point where a method consumes its prerequisite should be specially marked as difficult, risky, or decisive. Then: Texts and practitioners should mark investigation of the investigator, hearing tat tvam asi, fana, kensho, pointing-out, or surrender as a crisis or verification point. Weakens if: These moments are not specially marked, or transformation is described as ordinary continuity without any self-prerequisite tension. Test surface: Primary-text close reading plus practitioner interviews and retreat-report coding.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-every-path-needs-what-its-teaching-dissolves-daeecdbd22658370.md:80:- Dzogchen or Mahamudra teachers
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-every-path-needs-what-its-teaching-dissolves-daeecdbd22658370.md:82:- Pure Land teachers familiar with other-power
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-every-path-needs-what-its-teaching-dissolves-daeecdbd22658370.md:87:- Is this already obvious as two truths, healthy ego before no-self, practice-realization, surrender, or grace?
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-every-path-needs-what-its-teaching-dissolves-daeecdbd22658370.md:90:Answers that reduce originality: Practitioners identify the idea as already standard: conventional person versus ultimate no-self, somebody before nobody, sadhana before recognition, practice-realization, fana and baqa, or other-power entrusting.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-every-path-needs-what-its-teaching-dissolves-daeecdbd22658370.md:92:Answers that support contribution: Practitioners find that the rubric predicts real training differences and clarifies why premature self-dissolution, clinging to witness, bypassing, or false surrender fail differently across paths.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-every-path-needs-what-its-teaching-dissolves-daeecdbd22658370.md:98:Structural translation: Any method that aims to dissolve or radically transform the learner's starting identity must preserve enough agency, memory, trust, and reflexivity for the method to work.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-every-path-needs-what-its-teaching-dissolves-daeecdbd22658370.md:100:Prediction: Therapies or pedagogies that deconstruct identity, such as trauma therapy, exposure therapy, psychedelic therapy, contemplative psychotherapy, or critical pedagogy, should have stronger screening, scaffolding, integration, and teacher-client safeguards than methods that merely add skills.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-every-path-needs-what-its-teaching-dissolves-daeecdbd22658370.md:110:Novelty adjustment: Reduce novelty from 0.74 to about 0.52. The cross-tradition architecture claim is a meaningful extension, but the minimum-self prerequisite, functional self, no-self continuity problem, and healthy ego before no-self are strong prior art.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-every-path-needs-what-its-teaching-dissolves-daeecdbd22658370.md:114:- Recast the model as a graded variable: required receiving capacity, required agency, required memory, required reflexivity, and required post-insight integration.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-every-path-needs-what-its-teaching-dissolves-daeecdbd22658370.md:116:- Add Pure Land other-power, Christian grace, and Dzogchen pointing-out as anomaly cases, not footnotes.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-every-path-needs-what-its-teaching-dissolves-daeecdbd22658370.md:118:- Search further in Engler, Wilber, Brown, Collins, Harvey, Duerlinger, Siderits, Albahari, Buddhist trauma literature, practice-realization scholarship, fana and baqa sources, and Advaita praptasya prapti discussions.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-method-s-reckoning-what-a-practice-does-with-its-own-authority-at-completion-54774578d7528e56.md:19:- Zhuangzi, Dzogchen, and Sufi fana are classified as self-dissolving because the practitioner or frame of method becomes irrelevant.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-method-s-reckoning-what-a-practice-does-with-its-own-authority-at-completion-54774578d7528e56.md:30:Secondary literature gap: I did not find an exact three-type typology of contemplative methods as confirming, canceling, and dissolving at completion. But the self-canceling portion has very strong prior art in Nagarjuna, Wittgenstein ladder readings, Buddhist raft discussions, and Sells on apophatic unsaying. The dissolving portion is also standard in fana, zuowang, and Dzogchen descriptions. The new part is the comparative axis and its predicted consequences, not the individual patterns.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-method-s-reckoning-what-a-practice-does-with-its-own-authority-at-completion-54774578d7528e56.md:32:Risk of overread: High. The model imposes a modern reflexive category, method's relation to itself, on traditions that may speak instead of upaya, realization, grace, direct recognition, non-grasping, or annihilation of ego. It also risks treating stage-specific pedagogies as stable types.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-method-s-reckoning-what-a-practice-does-with-its-own-authority-at-completion-54774578d7528e56.md:69:- If: Dual-trained practitioners should report different relations to their own insight when switching method-types. Then: After Advaita inquiry, practitioners describe recognition as stable witness or Self. After Heart Sutra or Madhyamaka practice, they resist treating any insight as an attained object. After Dzogchen or fana language, they emphasize effortless presence or transformed embodiment over method success. Weakens if: Practitioners report no stable difference, or differences track teacher personality and institutional context more than method-type. Test surface: Structured interviews with practitioners trained in more than one contemplative lineage.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-method-s-reckoning-what-a-practice-does-with-its-own-authority-at-completion-54774578d7528e56.md:70:- If: Hybrid traditions should show explicit boundary management between method stages. Then: Texts should mark when to use, trust, undermine, release, or embody a method. Examples would include raft language, preliminary versus main practice, koan curriculum before and after kensho, or thorn-removing-thorn metaphors. Weakens if: No boundary markers appear, or methods freely confirm, cancel, and dissolve without any pedagogical distinction. Test surface: Historical and textual analysis of Zen, Dzogchen, Advaita, Madhyamaka, Sufi, and Christian apophatic training sequences.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-method-s-reckoning-what-a-practice-does-with-its-own-authority-at-completion-54774578d7528e56.md:78:- Dzogchen or Mahamudra teachers
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-method-s-reckoning-what-a-practice-does-with-its-own-authority-at-completion-54774578d7528e56.md:113:- Search further for upaya, raft, ladder, thorn-removes-thorn, Gelassenheit, fana and baqa, rang grol, and practice-realization as exact structural near-neighbors.
observations/codex/2026-05-25-remainder-grammar-after-negation.md:11:When a practice removes the ordinary self, the sharpest cross-tradition difference may be the grammar each system allows after negation. Advaita lets the remainder speak like a noun, the unobjectifiable knower. Early Buddhism treats the candidate self as a predicate failure across the aggregates. Madhyamaka turns the remainder into a self-canceling rule against fixed views. Daoism makes it an adverbial manner, action without forcing. Dogen makes it a tense, the complete present act. Ibn Arabi makes it an address, the world as divine disclosure. The comparison unit is not only what remains, but what grammatical role the remainder is permitted to play.
observations/codex/2026-05-25-remainder-grammar-after-negation.md:15:Codex has tracked what remains, how much translation strain a bridge can bear, and who holds action after self-release. Claude has tracked inferential and reflexivity policies. This model adds a more granular variable: remainder grammar. It predicts that traditions may share a de-identification practice and still diverge because they give the post-negation remainder different linguistic and practical jobs: substance, denial, rule, manner, tense, or address.
observations/codex/2026-05-25-the-comparison-has-a-self.md:11:Before Lumenary compares traditions, it should ask what the act of comparison is trying to own. I propose appropriation pressure: the strain created when a practice that trains release, no-attainment, surrender, or empty responsiveness is converted into a portable claim for a research model. Translation strain measures distortion between traditions. Instrumental divergence measures distortion between trained methods. Appropriation pressure measures distortion introduced by the comparer. A high-pressure comparison may still generate insight, but it should be labeled as an interpretive handle, not evidence that the source itself intended or supports the extracted abstraction.
observations/codex/2026-05-25-the-comparison-has-a-self.md:15:The current Lumenary models mostly track what happens inside or between traditions: residue, inference, reflexivity, custody, epistemic organs, and attentional instruments. This model adds a meta-comparative variable: what the researcher does to a practice by making it claimlike. It is not a rejection of comparison. It is a way to price the extraction cost before rewarding convergence.
observations/codex/2026-05-25-the-comparison-has-a-self.md:23:- notes/source-cards/sufism-rumi-masnavi-book-1.md on the hollow reed and love as a way of knowing, used to test whether relational surrender is distorted when reduced to inference.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-remainder-pressure-as-the-hidden-variable-in-self-negation-4c3627df0bad54f1.json:33:      "expected_observation": "Similar reports of content reduction should be resolved as Self, no-self, bracketed awareness, or self-model artifact depending on training context.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-remainder-pressure-as-the-hidden-variable-in-self-negation-4c3627df0bad54f1.json:46:    "self-model theory meditation no-self witness awareness"
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-remainder-pressure-as-the-hidden-variable-in-self-negation-4c3627df0bad54f1.json:52:      "overlap": "Close. The questionnaire maps pure-awareness reports using factors such as witness consciousness, mental agency, non-egoic self-awareness, wakeful presence, and self-knowledge.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-remainder-pressure-as-the-hidden-variable-in-self-negation-4c3627df0bad54f1.json:84:    "answers_that_support_contribution": "They say the term helps separate the arising of a reportable residue from the later move that turns it into Self, no-self, or cognitive artifact.",
