reviews/originality/2026-05-26-remainder-pressure-as-the-hidden-variable-in-self-negation-4c3627df0bad54f1.md:43:- Gamma and Metzinger, MPE-92M, https://pmc.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/articles/PMC8279394/: overlap: Close. The questionnaire maps pure-awareness reports using factors such as witness consciousness, mental agency, non-egoic self-awareness, wakeful presence, and self-knowledge.; difference: It does not frame these as pressure to posit a final subject after negation.; novelty impact: High reduction for the empirical-adjacent mechanism.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-remainder-pressure-as-the-hidden-variable-in-self-negation-4c3627df0bad54f1.md:63:- If: Training style should shape how the pressure is resolved, not whether the pressure can arise at all. Then: Similar reports of content reduction should be resolved as Self, no-self, bracketed awareness, or self-model artifact depending on training context. Weakens if: Training context predicts the entire phenomenology so strongly that no shared pressure stage can be identified. Test surface: Longitudinal study of practitioners cross-trained in Advaita and Buddhist methods.
